{%- comment -%}
  AVELO — CTA Band with animated wave top
  Black band with a curved/animated wave on its top edge, heading, subtext,
  and two outlined buttons. Mirrors the competitor's pre-footer CTA.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign cs = section.settings.color_scheme
-%}

